{"tid":1680253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「行動post」新死線->升級計劃書","createTime":"2019-10-28T16:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T14:02:43.000Z","uid":336524,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e674716d076825c4af862fc7c6a675688f1f3cba","tid":1680253,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:36:19.000Z","msg":"上一個post<br />\n「宣佈」政府若不在今個星期六之前宣佈成立獨立調查委員會調查警暴，我等將會行動升級。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1678499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1678499</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">整合</span></span><br />\n為左唔好阻到11.2 嘅集會<br />\n死線定係11.2 嘅晚上，如果政府未能係死線前做到我地嘅要求，我地將會係11.3 作為我地升級日。<br />\n<br />\n至於我地嘅要求暫時未能清晰定立，但係一定係圍繞懲罰黑警。//一齊討論下點定我地嘅要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫定要求政府即時成立獨立調查委員會調查警察濫權、違法嘅問題，並承諾會嚴懲犯罪的警察。<br />\n<br />\n如果政府真係成立調查委員會，可能我地過一個月又設死線，而且整合一堆已知及有證據嘅黑警犯案名單，要求政府必須係某月某日前以法律途徑嚴懲名單上的違法警察。務求逼政府確確實實懲罰黑警，否則我地將於制度外尋求公義。<br />\n<br />\n總之我地要keep住做死線-&gt;升級。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n升級方案<br />\n<br />\n11月3日起，<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n1）每逢遊行路經嘅閉路電視全部破壞，務求令警方無力追查示威者。</span><br />\n（若然係企係我地呢邊，或者唔想蒙受閉路電視被毁壞嘅損失，請於遊行當日收起閉路電視。）<br />\n我等保證絕不會向制裁名單以外的店鋪進行破壞，請放心收起閉路電視。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2）全民不論和勇必需跟隨dresscode。</span><br />\nDresscode<br />\n黑色衫蒙面；<br />\n//若使用面巾蒙面，被捉到之後你嘅面巾可成證物，因為面巾必定用來蒙面，但普通衫就唔一定。<br />\n自行權衡風險選擇用普通衫定面巾蒙面。//<br />\n<br />\n黑色短袖配黑色冰䄂/黑色長䄂衫；<br />\n黑色長褲；<br />\n黑色/灰色鞋；<br />\n黑色棒球帽；// 20$ 街市一頂<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3）請大家每人盡帶一啲工具。</span><br />\n<br />\n油類： 白電油、機油、花生油...<br />\n<br />\n白電油、機油難買啲但係用黎做彈嘅效果好<br />\n花生油方便易買但係用黎做彈麻麻地，只可以用黎燒rb,雜物。所以請盡買白電油、機油。<br />\n<br />\n毛巾（幫手整彈）//去五金鋪講要一打祝君好，50$ 就有一打祝君好牌毛巾。<br />\n<br />\n玻璃樽<br />\n<br />\n裝修工具：鐵筆、電批、士巴拿、六角匙...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Q&amp;A 關於爆閉路電視一事：</span></span><br />\nQ: 點解要爆閉路電視？<br />\nA: 等手足做野少一樣野顧慮，等多啲人願意成為勇武，達到全民皆兵，提升整體武力。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nQ: 爆左閉路電視咪好易比藍絲黑警嫁禍我地？<br />\nA: 我地係示威個陣需要監察有無人暴走亂打爛野，同埋制止一切想係勇武裝修完偷野嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n同埋，需要係升級日之前制定一份裝修名單。例如：我地於升級日只會裝修中銀、美心、360及政府相關建築，絕不會打攪其他店舖。<br />\n然後我地要嚴格執行呢份名單，就算中途發現一間好仆街嘅藍店都唔好搞，因為佢唔係我地嘅名單之上。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nQ:爆閉路電視咪對示威者少一樣保障囉？示威者比黑警暗角打、被自殺都無證據。<br />\nA:首先，好多時手足被狗捉到打都係因為落單、唔敢幫拖救人，如果大家爆閉路之後升級全民皆兵，絕對有效團結對抗黑警，減少被捕。<br />\n再者好多時啲人比黑警拉去暗角打，啲地方都無cctv，就算平時路中心手足比黑警私刑嘅片段都唔係靠cctv片段曝光，係靠在場記者/市民錄影揭發。所以從來cctv都無為我地提供過保障，只有負累。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">爆閉路嘅重要性。</span></span><br />\n1.）爆左之後黑警少左樣方法搵罪證。<br />\n如果有手足真係咁唔好彩比黑警拉到，黑警無cctv佐證又點告得入/告得重？<br />\n<br />\n2.）無咁易跟得到在場手足返屋企。<br />\n可能有手足驚做第一個爆閉路嘅人，但我想講就算你係第一個爆閉路嘅人，你爆個陣cctv影到晒你個樣，只要你個陣有好好地包得密實，佢地係無可能拉到你。影到你爆閉路嘅個條片只有當你比佢拉到，個陣先會對你不利。<br />\n否則係其他閉路都比其他手足打爆嘅情況下，只要你無比人即場拉、無比黑警跟返屋企，佢地無可能拉到你。因為你既有dresscode保護，黑警又無得靠睇cctv track 你行蹤，佢地係幾乎無可能拉到你。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰略重點及戰場</span></span><br />\n升級行動最重要應該係玻璃樽、油、毛巾。因為到時大家爆晒閉路電視，唔洗再驚扔完走左佬比差佬用cctv刮返出黎，所以到時火魔數量應該會大量提升。而且無左閉路電視嘅後顧之憂，<span style=\"color: red;\">hit and run會成為我地嘅主要戰略</span><br />\n預期目標係燒爆狗車、扔中green objects<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div><br />\n亦因為預期到時打游擊戰，屆時作戰場地會係港島、九龍、大西北三地。主要分3個主戰場而唔係18區開花，咁樣嘅話人數唔會太少導致某區太少人被圍捕，而且大家揀返近自己嘅主戰場容易be water。"},{"pid":"a02ce4eb44f8d660cc678429f026963866832dd0","tid":1680253,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁"},{"pid":"fbc0647781fee53ba181edcfd347b2a31be3c33c","tid":1680253,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:42:06.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"821948bece28554d5fe6e5ab3e0bbaf77c33bc2f","tid":1680253,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:42:17.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"7a9a00dbeb892c1993fc6048b5dd80d67e0023af","tid":1680253,"uid":218469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:43:37.000Z","msg":"P牌幫推"},{"pid":"9560ec99c8d9f4f66064b80fc769c761b554815b","tid":1680253,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a888fbd6fa4921a9ad40f1495fed2c3b9bcad4","tid":1680253,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:53:48.000Z","msg":"Why no ppl😞"},{"pid":"06ad6802d235d9335f63f12b303a5bd95782122b","tid":1680253,"uid":54207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:54:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4aa5ef7a4271303e03ab04c031c85d9bb3a9bd0a","tid":1680253,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06ad6802d235d9335f63f12b303a5bd95782122b","tid":1680253,"uid":54207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:54:00.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"唔該你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7ef116113d94d5acc70c8e9ea7eb7a6bb3cab0","tid":1680253,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:59:33.000Z","msg":"大家覺得無用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解無人幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6df0e3fa1d9a6d95ce90f957ed4ec87e096bd4a","tid":1680253,"uid":139190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:01:51.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n<br />\n同埋我覺得要升級到閒日做呢啲嘢 <br />\n咁先可以令香港人無咁易抽離 同埋影響力更大"},{"pid":"a883564d5a118571c3281465376f187db6ecb1da","tid":1680253,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6df0e3fa1d9a6d95ce90f957ed4ec87e096bd4a","tid":1680253,"uid":139190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:01:51.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n<br />\n同埋我覺得要升級到閒日做呢啲嘢 <br />\n咁先可以令香港人無咁易抽離 同埋影響力更大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:05:53.000Z","msg":"我都覺其實每次出黎都要爆閉路<br />\n咁樣先安全"},{"pid":"be3c111e9884ac9cffdc1e1cf2048eed752e7572","tid":1680253,"uid":321602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a37b3c7eb1c451dd4a42e1ae7acf29662a4f0b","tid":1680253,"uid":54207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4aa5ef7a4271303e03ab04c031c85d9bb3a9bd0a","tid":1680253,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06ad6802d235d9335f63f12b303a5bd95782122b","tid":1680253,"uid":54207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:54:00.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"唔該你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:18:40.000Z","msg":"講呢啲 <br />\n啲人瞓咗姐 冇事嘅"},{"pid":"0eb7317dfe5817ff900dcf80a92c0f11597deca7","tid":1680253,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:21:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇下啦<br />\n<br />\n【正視聽：反思行動及行動數量】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680287</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c62af57b501c6654ca03aa73f939f7da22e41c96","tid":1680253,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:25:23.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4e371659b055b0aa501f059a9d91f3cc60ba81ab","tid":1680253,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:25:54.000Z","msg":"同意計劃 要plan定3/11活動"},{"pid":"112f790fbe09ee5518af6c97af7e459f812af3bd","tid":1680253,"uid":13634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T22:04:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95334e8d811d7849efab6c6b0642edde4a0789d6","tid":1680253,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T22:13:11.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"41df856364998d8862b65550ec625da6cdb752e1","tid":1680253,"uid":152689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T22:17:50.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"3b5307a268eb50f631055dcfae62d5623639ec60","tid":1680253,"uid":30988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T22:18:41.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"c38fb5abf24c220cf2f81e98a9f136260741ef0b","tid":1680253,"uid":261470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T22:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68637a486861bd9029d716283e2903339524e7b","tid":1680253,"uid":254797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T23:47:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fc799e1fdd68f678e7bb8d397d3e826478b5389","tid":1680253,"uid":246279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T23:54:10.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fqHOgUj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfqHOgUj.jpg&h=7fc95e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oej5i7F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOej5i7F.jpg&h=4247b46e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7672edabd42327616ae459d35ed67c2d9d8a8ab4","tid":1680253,"uid":41507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T23:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}